  <subsection xml:id="common-mistakes-8">
            <title>Common Mistakes</title>
            <blockquote>
                <p><ul>
                    <li>
                        <p>Missing the recursive call.  Be sure to look for a call to the same method.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Getting confused about when a recursive method returns and what it returns.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Assuming you understand what the recursion is doing without tracing all of it.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul></p>
